 2022-12972022-12-02,  CH,  ,  , 
ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JASCHA JABES of Toronto, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Heather Kennedy, whose term has expired.
